Mike Brearley has broken the record for most ODIs (13) as captain for ENG, going past Mike Denness
Mike Brearley has broken the record for most ducks (3) in ODIs for ENG, going past Graham Barlow's 2
Chappell has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (2) for CAN, going past Dennis
